le = Ask Billboard : Taylor Swift Out-'Shake's Mariah Carey | author =Trust, Gary|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media| date = September 1, 2014 | accessdate = September 2, 2014}}</ref>\n|\n* [[Australian Recording Industry Association|ARIA]]: 3\u00d7 Platinum<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aria.com.au/pages/httpwww.aria.com.aupagesaria-charts-accreditations-singles-2014.htm|title=ARIA Charts \u2013 Accreditations \u2013 2014 Singles|accessdate=March 5, 2014|work=ARIA.com.au|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]}}</ref>\n* [[British Phonographic Industry|BPI]]: Platinum<ref name=\"bpi\">{{cite web|url=http://www.bpi.co.uk/certified-awards.aspx|title=Certified Awards Search: A Great Big World|publisher=[[British Phonographic Industry]]|accessdate=2014-04-04|format=To access, enter the search parameter \"A Great Big World\" and select \"Search by: Keyword\", with the other two set to \"All\"}}</ref>\n* [[Music Canada|MC]]: 6\u00d7 Platinum{{Certification Cite Ref|region=Canada|type=digital download|title=Say Something|artist=A Great Big World}}\n* [[Recording Industry Association of America|RIAA]]: 6\u00d7 Platinum{{Certification Cite Ref|region=United States|type=single|title=Say Something|artist=A GREAT BIG WORLD & CHRISTINA AGUILERA}}\n* [[Recorded Music NZ|RMNZ]]: Platinum<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=2432|title=NZ Top 40 Singles Chart|accessdate=March 8, 2014|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2014\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Already Home\"\n| \u2014 || 24 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Rockstar\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 86 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|\n|-\n| 2015\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Hold Each Other]]\"<br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Futuristic (rapper)|Futuristic]])</span>\n| 99 || 12 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 69 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|\n| rowspan=\"3\"| ''When the Morning Comes''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2016\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Oasis\"\n| \u2014 || 22 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Won't Stop Running\"\n| \u2014 || 34 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|\n|-\n| 2017\n! scope=\"row\"| \"When I Was a Boy\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|\n| rowspan=\"7\"| ''A Great Big World''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2018\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Younger\"\n| \u2014 || 18 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"You\"\n| \u2014 || 39 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2019\n! scope=\"row\"| \"This Is Magic\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Boys in the Street\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Fall on Me (Andrea Bocelli and Matteo Bocelli song)#A Great Big World and Christina Aguilera version|Fall on Me]]\"<br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(with Christina Aguilera)</span><ref>{{cite tweet|user=AGreatBigWorld|number=1196423372156145664|title=We are so excited to announce our newest collaboration #FallOnMe with @xtina!|date=November 18, 2019|accessdate=November 19, 2019}}</ref>\n| \u2014 || 37 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|\n|-\n| 2020\n! scope=\"row\"| \"I Will Always Be There\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/au/album/i-will-always-be-there-single/1504714322|title=i will always be there \u2013 Single by A Great Big World|website=Apple Music|accessdate=April 3, 2020}}</ref>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 