op Songs|US<br>Adult]]<br><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/a-great-big-world/chart-history/ATF|title=A Great Big World Chart History - Adult Pop Songs|work=Billboard|accessdate=January 28, 2020}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[ARIA Charts|AUS]]<br /><ref name=\"AUS\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[\u00d63 Austria Top 40|AUT]]<br /><ref name=\"AUT\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Canadian Hot 100|CAN]]<br /><ref name=\"CANSingles\">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/5885925/a-great-big-world/chart?f=793|title=A Great Big World \u2013 Chart history: Billboard Canadian Hot 100|work=Billboard}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Irish Singles Chart|IRE]]<br /><ref name=\"IRE\">{{cite web|url=http://irish-charts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=A+Great+Big+World|title=Discography A Great Big World|publisher=Irish Charts Portal. Hung Medien}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Japan Hot 100|JPN]]<br /><ref name=\"JPN-singles\">{{cite web |url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=a great big world|chart=Japan Hot 100}} |title=A Great Big World \u2013 Chart History: Japan Hot 100 |work=Billboard |accessdate=April 25, 2016}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Official New Zealand Music Chart|NZ]]<br /><ref name=\"NZ\">{{cite web|url=https://charts.nz/showinterpret.asp?interpret=A+Great+Big+World|title=Discography A Great Big World|publisher=New Zealand Charts Portal. Hung Medien}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Sverigetopplistan|SWE]]<br /><ref name=\"SWE\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%;\"| [[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/music-charts/ |title=Official Charts Company |work=officialcharts.com |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6KB4iRFFo?url=http://www.officialcharts.com/music-chart