[[Carolina Miranda (actress)|Carolina Miranda]] would replace Soto as the main protagonist and series title character in season three.<ref name=\"telemundo.com\">{{cite web|title=Inician las grabaciones de \"Se\u00f1ora Acero 3, La Coyote\"|url=http://www.telemundo.com/novelas/2016/05/12/inician-las-grabaciones-de-senora-acero-3-la-coyote|website=telemundo.com|accessdate=13 May 2016}}</ref>\n\n== Music ==\n;Track listing \n{{Track listing\n| collapsed       = \n| headline        = \n| extra_column    =\n\n| title1        =La Se\u00f1ora de Acero{{efn-ua|Main theme of season one.}} \n| note1          =[[Los Tucanes de Tijuana]]\n| length1        = 5:33\n\n| title2        =La venganza de Sarita{{efn-ua|Main theme of season two.}} \n| note2          =[[Los Tucanes de Tijuana]]\n| length2        = 4:33<ref>{{cite web|title=La Venganza De Sarita - Los Tucanes de Tijuana (2da. Temporada \"SE\u00d1ORA ACERO\")|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gVlw7PyhIks|website=youtube.com|accessdate=10 December 2017|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n\n| title3        =La Coyote{{efn-ua|Main theme of season three.}} \n| note3          =[[Los Tucanes de Tijuana]]\n| length3        = 5:35<ref>{{cite web|title=La Coyote - (Se\u00f1ora Acero 3) - Los Tucanes De Tijuana [Official Audio]|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PM-jKFsUUjw|website=youtube.com|accessdate=28 December 2017|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n\n| title4        =La justiciera de la frontera{{efn-ua|Main theme of season four.}} \n| note4          =[[Los Tucanes de Tijuana]]\n| length4        = 5:36<ref>{{cite web|title=La justiciera de la frontera - (Se\u00f1ora Acero 4) - Los Tucanes De Tijuana [Official Audio]|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zynH5Lyrl-4|website=youtube.com|accessdate=March 3, 2018|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n| title5        =Yo no pienso volver\n| note5          =[[Litzy]]\n| length5       = {{efn-ua|This song was never released in a single format, it was only created for the series and only small parts are heard.\n