 de Acero |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date= |website= |publisher=Super Latina TV |accessdate=August 23, 2014|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tvnotas.com.mx/2014/07/09/C-63833-video-primer-promocional-de-senora-acero-protagonizada-por-blanca-soto.php|title=VIDEO: Primer promocional de 'Se\u00f1ora Acero', protagonizada por Blanca Soto |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date= |website= |publisher=Revista TVnotas M\u00e9xico |accessdate=August 23, 2014|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n\nBlanca Soto departed from the series after season two and [[Carolina Miranda (actress)|Carolina Miranda]] would replace Soto as the main protagonist and series title character in season three.<ref name=\"telemundo.com\">{{cite web|title=Inician las grabaciones de \"Se\u00f1ora Acero 3, La Coyote\"|url=http://www.telemundo.com/novelas/2016/05/12/inician-las-grabaciones-de-senora-acero-3-la-coyote|website=telemundo.com|accessdate=13 May 2016}}</ref>\n\n== Music ==\n;Track listing \n{{Track listing\n| collapsed       = \n| headline        = \n| extra_column    =\n\n| title1        =La Se\u00f1ora de Acero{{efn-ua|Main theme of season one.}} \n| note1          =[[Los Tucanes de Tijuana]]\n| length1        = 5:33\n\n| title2        =La venganza de Sarita{{efn-ua|Main theme of season two.}} \n| note2          =[[Los Tucanes de Tijuana]]\n| length2        = 4:33<ref>{{cite web|title=La Venganza De Sarita - Los Tucanes de Tijuana (2da. Temporada \"SE\u00d1ORA ACERO\")|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gVlw7PyhIks|website=youtube.com|accessdate=10 December 2017|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n\n| title3        =La Coyote{{efn-ua|Main theme of season three.}} \n| note3          =[[Los Tucanes de Tijuana]]\n| length3        = 5:35<ref>{{cite web|title=La Coyote - (Se\u00f1ora Acero 3) - Los Tucanes De Tijuana [Official Audio]|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PM-jKFsUUjw|website=youtube.com|accessdate=28 December 2017|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n\n| title4  